    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Rasa,",
        "I am Sahar XXX , one of your student in evening course class. I am writing this letter to describe why I can not attend more in you interesting and knowledgeable course.",
        "As you know , I am a reservoir engineer and also I have a twins that they are three years old. The good news is that recently I got a promotion and now I am working as a lead of reservoir engineer but the bad point is that I am too busy now due to my promotion.",
        "would you remember that mostly I was overtime. Even I sometime had not do my homework. And now, the situation gets worse. My new responsibility requires to work overtime. Moreover, I have to attend more meetings that they can take several hours to reach suitable decisions. So if I have any spare time I prefer to spend it with my children.",
        "Unfortunately, I inclined to postpone my study to other more suitable time. In addition, last day I called to administration secretary and pressed her that I want the full refund of all the amount paid for enrolling this course and she told me it was possible only when your teacher sign you amendment letter. Dealing with mind the circumstance I trust that you will kindly sign my attached demand letter. I am pleasantly thankful for you kindness.",
        "Your sincerely,",
        "SaharXXX"
